dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.swcomponenttemplate.swcinternalbehavior

Interface IInternalBehavior

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable

    public interface IInternalBehavior
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IInternalBehavior: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    The internal behavior of an atomic software component describes the RTE relevant aspects of a component, i.e. the runnable entities and the events they respond to.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!

        boolean getSupportsMultipleInstantiation()
        Query the value of the attribute SupportsMultipleInstantiation.
